    <div class="about">
      <h3>ABOUT CLOUDCOMPUTING</h3>
      <p><strong>Cloud computing</strong>
        is the delivery of different services through the Internet. These
        resources include tools and applications like data storage, servers,
        databases, networking, and software. Cloud-based storage makes it
        possible to save files to a remote database and retrieve them on demand.
        Services can be both public and private</p>
