      <div class="content">
        <h3>OTHER SKILLS</h3>
        <p><strong>API and WEBSERVICES:</strong> XML, SOAP</p>
        <p><strong>Virtualization:</strong>EC2, Lambdas</p>
        <p>Networking</p>
        <p>Developmental Operations(DevOps)</p>
        <p>Information Security and Recovery</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h3>AVAILABLE CERTIFICATIONS</h3>
        <p>Amazon Web Services Certification</p>
        <p>Microsoft Azure Certification</p>
